{color:#6A7480}We add a Counter-guarantees object that lists the associated counter guarantees.{color}

{color:#6A7480}We need a list of all the counter-guarantees with the following info for each:{color}

* {color:#6A7480}Principal{color}
* {color:#6A7480}Reference Code{color}
* {color:#6A7480}Effective Date{color}
* {color:#6A7480}End Date{color}
* {color:#6A7480}Currency{color}
* {color:#6A7480}Amount{color}

{color:#6A7480}{color}

{color:#6A7480}Note: {color}

* {color:#6A7480}the Counter-guarantees object should be at the same level as "Characteristics" {color}

h4. Note
 * There will be no pagination for the V1
 * We should limit the response to max 25k guarantee (or less if this brings perf issues)

